des:
Pawcatuck and North Stonington Little League Tee Ball division games schedule by the next game number. Game times, ballfield, and opponent teams are provided. No personal information is being used within this skill and is nothing is being collected or saved. Teams are now using four fields so providing a nice service to reduce parents texting or emailing coaches this skill technology is very impressive, simple aide to help team parents find their ballfield when they arrive at the games. Say your team name to hear the next time, field, and opponent your team is playing. 
Team Names include;
Dairy Queen
Mystic Diner
The Tin Peddler
Norwich Orthopedic Group
Jewett City Savings Bank
Stonington Pizza
Stonington Historical Society
Buzzi Memorials
